        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Can you add this patch here?\r\n\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/runtime/doc/lsp.txt b/runtime/doc/lsp.txt\r\nindex 9164299c1b..b4fe723182 100644\r\n--- a/runtime/doc/lsp.txt\r\n+++ b/runtime/doc/lsp.txt\r\n@@ -717,7 +717,7 @@ LspProgress                                                       *LspProgress*\r\n         vim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('LspProgress', { buffer = buf, callback = function(ev)\r\n             local value = ev.data.params.value\r\n             vim.api.nvim_echo({ { value.message or 'done' } }, false, {\r\n-              id = ev.data.id,\r\n+              id = string.format(\"lsp: %d\", ev.data.client_id),\r\n               kind = 'progress',\r\n               source = 'vim.lsp',\r\n               title = value.title,\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontext: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38514#discussion_r3005704989",
